      <h1 class="text-3xl md:text-5xl font-bold leading-tight mb-6">
        AI Doesn't Take Your Job—It Makes You the CEO. But Only Within Trusted Tribes
      </h1>
      <div class="flex items-center gap-4 text-gray-400 text-sm border-t border-white/10 pt-6">
        <span>Lisa Tamati</span>
        <span class="text-white/20">|</span>
        <span>19/04/2026</span>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="mb-12 rounded-2xl overflow-hidden border border-white/10">
      <img
        src="/blog/ptl-balaji-ai-trusted-tribes.png"
        alt="Human figures connected to an AI circuit network — chaos on one side, structured complexity on the other"
        class="w-full object-cover"
